    "description": "Are you a skilled Surgeon looking for your next big career move? Piramal Pharma in Nagpur offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Piramal Pharma:\nPiramal Pharma is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Piramal Pharma!",
